#: ../../content/applications/general/iot/config/troubleshooting.rst:612
msgid "Follow the instructions, along with the following process:"
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/general/iot/config/troubleshooting.rst:614
msgid ""
"Hold the **>T<** button for eight seconds, or until :guilabel:`CONF` "
